<description>Do you want more customers for free? Just ask your current customers to refer their friends. When was the last time you asked? It's really that simple. How to get your customers to refer their friend: Ask nicely Don't screw...</description>
<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Do you want more customers for free?&nbsp; Just ask your current customers to refer their friends.&nbsp; </p> <p>When was the last time you asked?</p> <p>It's really that simple. </p> <p>How to get your customers to refer their friend:</p> <ol> <li>Ask nicely</li> <li>Don't screw it up with some complicated referral or rewards program</li> <li>Ask again, every so often</li> <li>Say thank you</li></ol> <p>Here's a great example from <a href="http://www.smartbrief.com/socialmedia/index.jsp?campaign=pardw">SmartBrief</a> (click for a close up):</p> <p><a href="http://www.damniwish.com/WindowsLiveWriter/image3_3.png"><img height="112" width="244" border="0" src="http://www.damniwish.com/WindowsLiveWriter/image3_thumb_2.png" alt="image" style="border: 0px none ; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px;" /></a> </p> <p><a href="http://www.damniwish.com/WindowsLiveWriter/image_145.png"><img height="102" width="244" border="0" src="http://www.damniwish.com/WindowsLiveWriter/image_thumb_103.png" alt="image" style="border: 0px none ; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px;" /></a></p><div class="feedflare">
